https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API

Paper.js: 
an open source vector graphics scripting framework that runs on top of the HTML5 Canvas. 
It offers a clean Scene Graph / Document Object Model and a lot of powerful functionality 
to create and work with vector graphics and bezier curves(贝塞尔曲线), 
all neatly wrapped up in a well designed, consistent and clean programming interface.

http://paperjs.org/tutorials/getting-started/working-with-paper-js/

http://paperjs.org/tutorials/interaction/keyboard-interaction/

https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/howler/2.0.12/howler.js

Howler.js has updated their syntax:
var sound = new Howl({
  src: ['sound.mp3']
});
sound.play();

